MENU_PKG_WEBKIT
  Here you will find all options concerning WebKit

SDECFG_PKG_WEBKIT_LIB
  Build either with GTK+, Qt4 or QtCore

SDECFG_PKG_WEBKIT_LIBS_ONLY
  Build only WebCore libs without Qt apps
